        <briefdescription>
<para>Delayed &apos;minimum values&apos; operation. The dimension, along which the minima are found, is set via &apos;dim&apos;. For dim = 0, the minimum value of each column is found (i.e. searches by traversing across rows). For dim = 1, the minimum value of each row is found (i.e. searches by traversing across columns). The default is dim = 0. </para>        </briefdescription>
